<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Return Gift Ideas | Gender Reveal</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Gender Reveal return gift ideasCss.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css"/>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero-section-genderrevealretgifts">
    <div class="hero-content-genderrevealretgifts fade-in-up">
      <h1>Thoughtful Return Gifts</h1>
      <p>Send your guests home with a smile and a beautiful keepsake.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Return Gift Ideas Slider -->
  <section class="section-genderrevealretgifts fade-in-up">
    <h2>Memorable Return Gifts</h2>
    <div class="swiper returnGiftSlider">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/Candles.jpeg" alt="Candles">
          <h3>Scented Candles</h3>
          <p>Personalized mini candles with pastel labels add warmth and charm to your event.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/honey jar (3).jpeg" alt="Honey Jar">
          <h3>Mini Honey Jars</h3>
          <p>“Sweet as can bee” jars are cute, meaningful, and perfect for thank-you favors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/Succulent Party Favors.jpeg" alt="Succulent">
          <h3>Succulent Plants</h3>
          <p>Eco-friendly and adorable — let your love grow with mini succulents.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/cookie packets.jpeg" alt="Cookies">
          <h3>Cookie Packs</h3>
          <p>Pretty cookies in pink and blue packaging — delicious and decorative!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/soap gift.jpeg" alt="Soap">
          <h3>Handmade Soaps</h3>
          <p>Pastel soaps wrapped with ribbon bring a gentle, luxurious touch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide card-genderrevealretgifts">
          <img src="/img/mini picture album.jpeg" alt="Soap">
          <h3>Mini Picture Albums</h3>
          <p>Compact, beautifully designed photo albums that guests can use to store memories from the event.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
      <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
      <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tips -->
  <section class="section-genderrevealretgifts fade-in-up tips-box-genderrevealretgifts">
    <h2>FIORE’s Gift Tips</h2>
    <ul>
  <li> Consider coordinating the gift packaging with the colors and theme of your gender reveal celebration to create a cohesive and memorable experience for your guests.</li>
  <li> Add a personal touch by attaching a heartfelt thank-you tag or a cute, baby-themed sticker to each gift, making them feel even more special and personalized.</li>
  <li> Choose practical, eco-friendly, and meaningful gifts that guests will treasure, ensuring your thoughtful gesture lingers long after the event.</li>
  <li> Arrange the gifts in an elegant, decorative basket or tray to make it easy for guests to pick up their favor while adding a touch of charm to your display.</li>
  <li> For an extra touch of elegance, consider adding custom ribbons or soft pastel wrapping that complements the aesthetic of your gender reveal party.</li>
  <li> Make each return gift unique by offering personalized options, such as customized keychains or small photo frames, that will remind guests of the joyous occasion.</li>
  <li> Include a thoughtful note or message inside the gift, expressing your gratitude for their attendance and making them feel even more appreciated.</li>
  <li> If your event has a theme (like "Sweet as Can Bee" or "Twinkle Twinkle Little Star"), ensure that your return gifts match the theme for a fully immersive experience.</li>
  <li> Keep the gifts practical but chic — consider elegant, high-quality items such as artisanal soaps, small potted plants, or luxury candles that reflect your sophisticated style.</li>
</ul>
  </section>


  <!-- Swiper & Animation Script -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    const swiper = new Swiper('.returnGiftSlider', {
      loop: true,
      spaceBetween: 30,
      slidesPerView: 1,
      navigation: {
        nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
        prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev'
      },
      pagination: {
        el: '.swiper-pagination',
        clickable: true
      },
      breakpoints: {
        640: { slidesPerView: 1 },
        768: { slidesPerView: 2 },
        1024: { slidesPerView: 3 }
      }
    });

    const faders = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in-up');
    const appearOptions = { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: "0px 0px -50px 0px" };
    const appearOnScroll = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries, observer) {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
        entry.target.classList.add('appear');
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      });
    }, appearOptions);
    faders.forEach(f => appearOnScroll.observe(f));
  </script>

</body>
</html>
